## ğŸ“Š Overview
The **Regional KPI Dashboard** is an interactive Tableau dashboard designed to analyze and compare regional business performance across key metrics. It enables users to evaluate **Sales, Profit, Orders, and Customers** over time, benchmark results against the prior year, and drill down geographically from region to state and city levels.

This dashboard is ideal for executive reporting, regional performance reviews, and operational decision-making.

